Oracle Big Data Spatial and Graph Raster Analysis Java API Reference

This document is the API specification for the Raster Analysis Framework, that allows you to create loader and processor job instances to execute raster analysis in parallel. This API is useful to create jobs that may be exposed as a Web Service and you may find some examples on how to create your own jobs from different perspectives on Oracle Big Data Spatial install directory under /opt/oralce/oracle-spatial-graph/spatial/raster/examples.
